node.text:
500 million people meditate worldwide. Boxer and trainer @patricia_domingo didn’t used to be one of them—but that changed when she tried these techniques for herself. 
On this episode of UA Body In Mind, Patricia connects with Peloton instructor @emmalovewell and sports psychologist Rebecca Levett to learn how meditation techniques can help her focus, feel calm, and power through her day.

Train your mind at the UA Performance Academy at performanceacademy.ua.com

Boxer and trainer @patricia_domingo is ready to take her training to the next level, and we’re here to make it happen. 
Introducing our newest series, UA Body In Mind, where Under Armour connects Patricia with our top women athletes and experts to train her body and mind. With the help of sports psychologist Rebecca Levett and WNBA player @bella_alarie, see how Patricia learns to use “self talk” to take her performance to the next level. 

Train your mind at the UA Performance Academy: performanceacademy.ua.com
